user_prompt_template:
Generate a Pharmodle puzzle for the drug: {drug_name}

Drug details:
- AMH Chapter: {chapter}
- Drug class-mates (same class): {classmates}
- Assigned puzzle type: {type}
- Difficulty target: {difficulty}

Puzzle type instructions:
{type_instructions}

Clue labels for this type: {clue_labels}

IMPORTANT REMINDERS:
- The answer "{drug_name}" must NEVER appear in any clue text (check carefully!)
- No brand names of {drug_name} in clues 1-4
- No other specific drug names in clues 1-4
- No drug class name in clues 1-2
- Every fact must be pharmacologically accurate
- Clue 1 should be genuinely broad (10+ drugs could fit)

Respond with this exact JSON structure:
{{
  "answer": "{drug_name}",
  "aliases": ["brand names", "alternative generic names"],
  "acceptable_alternatives": [],
  "near_misses": {{
    "drugs": ["class-mate drugs ruled out by specific clues"],
    "feedback": "1 sentence explaining why answer is correct and near-misses are wrong"
  }},
  "category": "therapeutic category",
  "domain": "specific domain",
  "type": "{type}",
  "difficulty": "{difficulty}",
  "clues": [
    {{"label": "{label1}", "text": "15-60 words"}},
    {{"label": "{label2}", "text": "15-60 words"}},
    {{"label": "{label3}", "text": "15-60 words"}},
    {{"label": "{label4}", "text": "15-60 words"}},
    {{"label": "{label5}", "text": "15-60 words"}}
  ],
  "explanation": "2-3 sentences",
  "confidence": 5
}}
